{{#section "plaintext-body"}}
Hi {{{_person.firstName}}},

A new mobile device was used to sign into your Arcus account. If you are aware of this change, please disregard this email. 

By default, this device will now receive your push notifications. Edit these settings by going to Settings > Profile > Push Notifications. 

If you did not recently sign into your Arcus account from a new mobile device, your account may have been compromised. 

{{/section}}

